---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@/components/Header';
import Footer from '@/components/Footer';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Snake Catcher Sunshine Coast | Professional Snake Removal – Woods Wildlife"
  description="Mudjimba-based Sunshine Coast snake catcher providing fast, professional snake removal and relocation. Call now for prompt response."
  canonical="/snake-catching-sunshine-coast/"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <Header client:load />

    <!-- Page Title Section -->
    <section class="container py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
          Professional Snake Catcher – Sunshine Coast
        </h1>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          <p>Woods Wildlife provides licensed snake removal and safe relocation across the Sunshine Coast. All snakes are captured and relocated in accordance with Queensland wildlife regulations.</p>
          <p>We respond quickly across Mudjimba, Marcoola, Twin Waters, Mt Coolum and surrounding suburbs.</p>
          <p>If you've seen a snake on your property, keep your distance and call for professional removal.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
          Our Snake Removal Process
        </h2>
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-foreground text-base mb-10 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Fast response to your location</li>
          <li>Safe inspection of the property</li>
          <li>Professional capture</li>
          <li>Humane relocation</li>
          <li>Advice to reduce future encounters</li>
        </ol>

        <a
          href="tel:0435529657"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-base font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
          0435 529 657
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Snake Catching & Relocation -->
    <section class="bg-card">
      <div class="container py-20 md:py-28">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
            Snake Catching & Relocation – Sunshine Coast
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-5 text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            <p>Snake activity is common across the Sunshine Coast, particularly in coastal and bushland suburbs during warmer months.</p>
            <p>Snakes are often encountered in:</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-foreground text-base mb-8">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Yards and garden beds</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Garages and sheds</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Roof cavities</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Retaining walls</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Around water sources and vegetation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">Woods Wildlife provides:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-foreground text-base mb-8">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Safe snake capture</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Responsible relocation in accordance with Queensland wildlife regulations</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Residential and commercial response</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Practical advice to reduce future encounters</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Fully insured service</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Our focus is safe capture and professional handling in line with state wildlife requirements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What To Do -->
    <section class="container py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
          What To Do If You See a Snake
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          <p>If you encounter a snake on your property:</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-foreground text-base mb-8">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Stay calm and keep your distance</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Bring pets and children indoors</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Do not attempt to move or kill the snake</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Keep visual contact only if safe</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span>&#8226;</span>Contact a licensed snake catcher immediately</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          <p>Attempting to handle a snake without training is dangerous and increases risk.</p>
          <p>Woods Wildlife provides prompt snake response across Mudjimba and surrounding northern Sunshine Coast suburbs.</p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="tel:0435529657"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-base font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
          0435 529 657
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mudjimba Based -->
    <section class="bg-card">
      <div class="container py-20 md:py-28">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
            Mudjimba Based – Servicing Northern Sunshine Coast
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-5 text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            <p>Woods Wildlife is based in Mudjimba and focuses on fast response across nearby suburbs including:</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-mudjimba" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Mudjimba →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-marcoola" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Marcoola →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-twin-waters" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Twin Waters →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-pacific-paradise" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Pacific Paradise →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-mt-coolum" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Mt Coolum →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-bli-bli" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Bli Bli →</a></li>
            <li><a href="/snake-catcher-coolum" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catcher Coolum →</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            As a local operator, we understand the coastal environment where snake activity is most common — particularly near bushland, dunes, wetlands and residential gardens.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mt-8 mb-6">
            If your suburb isn't listed, we still service the entire Sunshine Coast. Call now for fast local response.
          </p>
          <a
            href="tel:0435529657"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-base font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
            Call 0435 529 657
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-card">
      <div class="container py-20 md:py-28">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
            Services &amp; Locations
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li><a href="/snake-catching-sunshine-coast" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Snake Catching &rarr;</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">Contact Woods Wildlife &rarr;</a></li>
            <li><a href="/locations" class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors">View All Locations &rarr;</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
      <div class="container py-20 md:py-28">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary-foreground">
            Snake Catcher Near Me – Sunshine Coast
          </h2>
          <p class="text-primary-foreground/70 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto">
            If you are searching for a snake catcher near you on the Sunshine Coast, Woods Wildlife provides professional snake removal across Mudjimba and surrounding northern suburbs. For urgent response, call directly.
          </p>
          <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-foreground">
            0435 529 657
          </p>
          <p class="text-primary-foreground/60 text-sm mb-10">Available 24/7 for urgent snake removal.</p>
          <a
            href="tel:0435529657"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary-foreground text-primary px-10 py-4 rounded-lg text-base font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
            Call Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer client:load />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
